{"lemma":"طالِعٌ","slug":"طالِعٌ","root":"ط.ل.ع","root_slug":"ط-ل-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ط-ل-ع","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n26955"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B7%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%90%D8%B9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"omen"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"luck","tags":["uncountable"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to read"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to study"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to look at, examine"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"active participle of طَلَعَ (ṭalaʕa)","tags":["active","form-of","participle"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of the verb طَلَعَ (ṭalaʕa, “to appear”)."},"ipa":["/tˤaː.liʕ/","/tˤaː.la.ʕa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n26955","headword_ar":"طَالِعٌ","root":"TlE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rising,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appearing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as a star &c.:] anything"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appearing from the upper part"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that comes up out of a thing and appears"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appearing by rising,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by becoming elevated."},{"kind":"text","text":"(See 1.)] ―         -b2-  [Hence,] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAliEuhu saEiydN","text_ar":"طَالِعُهُ سَعِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His star"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is fortunate"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  [Hence also,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~aAliEu","text_ar":"الطَّالِعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The false dawn:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~aAliEu AlmuSoEidu","text_ar":"الطَّالِعُ المُصْعِدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hilaAl","text_ar":"هِلَال"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"moon when near the sun, showing a narrow rim of light;"},{"kind":"text","text":"probably"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the new moon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"from the sight of which the commencement of the month was reckoned; as appears from what follows]. (O, K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA raA^ayotuka muno*u TaAliEayoni","text_ar":"مَا رَاَيْتُكَ مُنْذُ طَالِعَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is mentioned as heard from some of the Arabs of the desert, meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muno*u $ahorayoni","text_ar":"مُنْذُ شَهْرَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have not seen thee for two months,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"during the period since two new moons"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O.) ―         -b5-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The arrow that falls behind the butt:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that passes beyond the butt, going over it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and Kt says that they used to reckon that falling above the mark as that which hit the butt: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TawaAliEu","text_ar":"طَوَالِعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, TA.) It is said of one of the kings, accord. to Sgh, [in the O,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAna yasojudu lilT~aAliEi","text_ar":"كَانَ يَسْجُدُ لِلطَّالِعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) meaning as expl. in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sjd","text_ar":"سجد"},{"kind":"text","text":": (O, TA: *) or it may mean that"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he used to lower himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bend himself down, to the rising"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hilaAl","text_ar":"هِلَال"},{"kind":"text","text":", by way of magnifying God. (O, TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAliEapu AlA_ibili","text_ar":"طَالِعَةُ الاـِبِلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The first,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foremost, of the camels."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","S","Az","O","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}